{"tid":455050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT 狗] 要借我隻 windows usb, 俾返車錢我喎","createTime":"2017-11-01T17:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T01:01:59.000Z","uid":5004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5509c5644edf9f4b4b9a8966875ea7419fa977","tid":455050,"uid":5004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:32:58.000Z","msg":"朋友小本生意賣下二手廠機同電腦維修，有日同我分享一件事，聽完真係覺得低賤既香港人搞到 IT 係香港既地位好低賤<br />\n<br />\n佢半年前賣左部機俾條友，私保三星期。條友開頭已經嫌呢樣嫌果樣，又嫌貴，講價，講價唔成就話 &quot;我落 ssp 買好過！&quot;, 結果過幾日條友死死地氣返黎搵我朋友買機，咁見有生意咪照賣囉<br />\n<br />\n賣完相安無事左半年，條友呢兩日突然同我朋友講部機有問題, 想 format 部機再裝過。詳情請睇佢 cap 俾我既圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/013200_b5a8e1390fb3d01e7ea0e9ca0c18c77d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F013200_b5a8e1390fb3d01e7ea0e9ca0c18c77d.jpg&h=18dad101&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/013201_0d8a48d6bbbd9706e013a891f35c762f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F013201_0d8a48d6bbbd9706e013a891f35c762f.jpg&h=59b647f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/013202_0c2b5998a7dab4f747f24c71fd73ed08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F013202_0c2b5998a7dab4f747f24c71fd73ed08.jpg&h=bc5a0202&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/013202_e47d32a5a01f6e738a911e0da0cf81b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F013202_e47d32a5a01f6e738a911e0da0cf81b4.jpg&h=06037fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/013203_f203a572352b0ab535bafdd2a7b4deac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F013203_f203a572352b0ab5